      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts up without hesitation and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, making it an excellent candidate for a dependable daily driver. The interior is clean with only minor signs of use, and while there are a few small scratches on the exterior paint, the body remains in great overall shape. All essential electronics and safety features are fully functional, offering a comfortable and safe driving experience.",
