      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, maintaining its original factory luster without a single swirl mark, door ding, or stone chip. The interior is a masterclass in preservation, featuring supple, unmarked leather, pristine carpets protected by original mats, and that unmistakable new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive history folder included. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched factory tool kit, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a flawless 'time capsule' example. No accidents, no modifications, and no compromises\u2014simply the finest specimen available on the market today.",
      "price": 47900.0,
