    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve taken such good care of it that it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly flawless condition\u2014not a single scratch or blemish to be found anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior is still spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
